name: PlanWavez MashUp x Hurric4n3Ike x Wayak x Benny Groove

metadata.name: PlanWavez MashUp x Hurric4n3Ike x Wayak x Benny Groove #1
metadata.description:
Presenting the culmination of the 'PlanWavez' saga. The 'PlanWavez' Mashup. Hurric4n3, Wayak, and Benny each made their own renditions of the legendary end of the year classic, PlanWavez. These songs are meant to usher in a new plan for music and Web3. To really help the world UNDERSTAND. The songs were then all put together to make this timeless mashup. God Bless the PLAN. Happy WavyWednesday Fam. 

This song is also Hurric4n3Ike's first drop on the iconic Sound.xyz and this 1/1 is a gift to the winner of the golden egg which is Jadyn Violet, a legend in the Web 3 space who is DEFINITELY sticking to his PLAN.
